Detailed Description

cvmx_gser::_sata_lane::_tx_amp#

SATA lane TX launch amplitude at Gen 1, 2 and 3 speeds. * AMP(0) is for Gen1. * AMP(1) is for Gen2. * AMP(2) is for Gen3.
